#MAE Mean Absolute Error

MAE<-function(actual,predicted){
  mean(abs(actual-predicted))
}
print("Error de prediccin del modelo")
## [1] "Error de prediccin del modelo"
MAE(p.rpart,wine_test$quality)
## [1] 0.6192157
